<p class=3D"center"><img src=3D"https://www.mathsisfun.com/algebra/images/t=
ransform-rotate.svg" alt=3D"A Rotation Transformation" height=3D"241" width=
=3D"212"></p>=20
<p>&nbsp;</p>=20
<p>Let us work through the mathematics to find out:</p>=20
<p>First calculate <span class=3D"center large">A =E2=88=92 =CE=BBI</span>:=
</p>=20
<p><br></p>=20
<div style=3D"text-align: center;">=20
<div class=3D"mat">=20
<div class=3D"cols2">=20
<div><span class=3D"intbl"><em>=E2=88=9A3</em><strong>2</strong></span></di=
v>
<div><span class=3D"intbl"><em>=E2=88=921</em><strong>2</strong></span></di=
v>
<div><span class=3D"intbl"><em>1</em><strong>2</strong></span></div>
<div><span class=3D"intbl"><em>=E2=88=9A3</em><strong>2</strong></span></di=
v>
